  "texts": [
    "DatasetDue to the scarcity of high-quality 3D scene-language data, we collect and construct a comprehensive 3D scene-language instruction dataset with GPT4-API.",
    "The dataset covers 1514 3D scenes of Scannet and encompasses 75K 3D scenelanguage pairs for 3D VQA, 3D Scene Captioning, 3D Grounding, and 3D Conversation task.",
    "Table 1 presents a detailed breakdown of the dataset, delineating the quantity of data for each respective task.",
    "3D VQA, Captioning and ConversationsBased on ScanQA [13] and ScanRefer [9], we collect and construct Instruction -Answer pairs with GPT-API.",
    "We utilize the caption of each object and generate corresponding questions."
  ],
